#: index.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colors"
msgstr "Amabara"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:303
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Black on White"
msgid "Black on white"
msgstr "Umukara ku Mweru"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:305
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many people with reduced vision find black text on a white screen gives the "
"most contrast, and is easiest to read. If this applies to you, you can set "
"this here."
msgstr ""
"Abantu Na: Gushaka umukara Umwandiko ku A Umweru Mugaragaza i "
"Inyuranyamigaragarire , na ni Kuri Soma . iyi Kuri , Gushyiraho iyi . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:312
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "White on Black"
msgid "White on black"
msgstr "Umweru ku Mukara"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:314
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many other people with reduced vision find the opposite to be true, that "
"white text on a black screen is easier to read."
msgstr ""
"Ikindi Abantu Na: Gushaka i Kuri nibyo , Umweru Umwandiko ku A umukara "
"Mugaragaza ni Kuri Soma . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Ibisanzwe"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:322
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Still other people find that pure black and white, in either order, is "
"difficult to read. You can set custom colors here for both the "
"<guilabel>Background</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Foreground</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Ikindi Abantu Gushaka umukara na Umweru , in Itondekanya , ni Kuri Soma . "
"Gushyiraho Guhanga Amabara ya:  Byombi i <guilabel> </guilabel> na i "
"<guilabel> </guilabel> . "

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:330
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use same color for all text"
msgstr "Gukoresha ibara rimwe ku mwandiko wose"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:332
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Many web sites use a different, often contrasting color for headings or "
"other flourishes. If this interferes with your ability to read the content, "
"you can enable this check box to have &kde; use the colors you have set "
"above for all text."
msgstr ""
"Urubuga Koresha A , Ibara: ya:  Imitwe Cyangwa Ikindi . iyi Na: Kuri Soma i "
